subject: Soccer
Courts
lead_paragraph: A judge on London’s High Court ruled Wednesday against attempts by the outgoing American co-owners, Tom Hicks and George Gillett Jr., to prevent the sale of Liverpool F.C. But the matter is not likely to end there.
